---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/Base.astro';
const pageTitle = "Misc";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle} category='misc'>
  <p class="text-center display-6">A landing page for my various microprojects</p>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h2 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-calculator"></i> ChemCalc</h2>
      <p class="card-text">A simple chemical calculator for calculating molar masses and balancing chemical equations. Supports fractional indices (e.g., for hydrates and nonstoichiometric compounds). Fully client-side (works offline in your browser). Written in <i class="bi bi-filetype-js"></i> JS, hosted on <i class="bi bi-git"></i> Gitlab Pages.</p>
      <p class="card-text"><a href="https://chemcalc.xyz/" target="_blank" class="card-link">chemcalc.xyz</a> (or, formerly, <a href="https://voffch.gitlab.io/" target="_blank">voffch.gitlab.io</a> if accessible)</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card mt-3">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h2 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-flower1"></i> A Secret Project</h2>
      <p class="card-text">In a <i class="bi bi-github"></i> Secret Garden grows a secret project, which I won't call by its proper name here because I don't think anything good will come out of its being known to a lot of people.</p>
      <p class="card-text"><a href="https://voffch.github.io/skotus/" target="_blank" class="card-link">so here's the link</a> (psst! don't tell anybody!)</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="text-center display-6 mt-3">and submicroprojects</p>
  <div class="list-group">
    <a href="https://voffch.github.io/periodic-table/" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
      <i class="bi bi-table"></i> Periodic Table
    </a>
    <a href="/vision#vision-checker" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
      <i class="bi bi-eyeglasses"></i> Test your visual acuity (no, seriously)
    </a>
    <a href="/single-pages/ojs2crossref.html" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
      <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-code"></i> OJS2 + Crossmark + Crossref = ðŸ’”
    </a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
